>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. MAIN.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 TMP0 PIC S9.
01 TMP1 PIC S9.
01 TMP2 PIC S9.
01 TMP3 PIC X.
01 TMP4 PIC X(100).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE -1 TO TMP0
    IF TMP0 < 0
        COMPUTE TMP1 = FUNCTION LENGTH("hello")
        ADD TMP1 TO TMP0
    END-IF
    COMPUTE TMP2 = TMP0 + 1
    MOVE "hello"(TMP2:1) TO TMP3
    MOVE TMP3 TO TMP4
    DISPLAY TMP4
    STOP RUN.
